conwaygame is a C++ simulation for Conway's Game of Life.

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway's_Game_of_Life

conwaygame requires C++11 and Qt5.


Install
-------

./configure
make
make install


To build and run the tests the following libraries are required:
- libunittest (http://libunittest.sourceforge.net)

conwaygame is being developed by Christian Blume. Contact Christian at
chr.blume@gmail.com for any questions or comments.
